name: Portrait of John S. Hougham in 1894

desc.html: This photograph is from archives of Alfred H. Mikesell (01/28/1914-06/25/2008), inherited from his mother, Hespera Hougham (07/22/1889 - 11/06/1958), who was the daughter of John S Hougham). Photo taken in 1894. Photographer unknown.
